item.description:
Dance at Princeton Station

Saturday Dec. 17th. 7:30 pm. for dinner, 9 pm for dancing.

Princeton Station

http://www.rockcityband.com/

147 Princeton St., N. Chelmsford, Ma.

Dress is casual and there is no cover charge.

Host: Steve Obermiller   603-491-1962    ob@tds.net 

       Join Steve O. and friends for a fun night of dancing to the music of Rock City playing tonight at Princeton Station! Steve will be there for dinner at 7:30, to hold seats, and also to introduce people. If you wish to join him for dinner? Please contact Steve and let him know. If you plan to join us for dinner, or just for dancing. Otherwise, we will do our best to hold on to seats. But, we can not be sure you will have seat So, please get there as early as you can.
item.how_to_find_us: Look 4 the Meetup signs on our tables
